name: JAGADITHA
description:
JAGADITHA means prosperity, peaceful and happiness from which Hinduism belief. 
In this world, Samsara haunt humans and bring miserable for humankind. Brahman (Bodhisattva) will neutralize and save the world.

In this art, Leak (Evil creature from Bali) represents Samsara and the Bali woman has its word, beautiful.
Bodhisattva will bring back a beautiful world.

Size 2000x2500 px
